  "Description": {
    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-technology\">long range</span> starship weapon, capable of delivering a highly explosive torpedo across massive distances.<br><br>Note: explosive damage is <span class=\"name name-stellar\">highly effective</span> against <span class=\"name name-stellar\">unshielded</span> targets, but <span class=\"name name-title\">ineffective</span> against <span class=\"name name-title\">shielded</span> targets.<br><br>Use <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span> to change weapon mode. Press <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span> to fire.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">远距离</span>飞船武器，能够远距离投掷高爆鱼雷。<br><br>注意：爆炸伤害对<span class=\"name name-stellar\">无护盾</span>目标<span class=\"name name-stellar\">非常有效</span>，但是对<span class=\"name name-title\">有护盾</span>目标<span class=\"name name-title\">没有效果</span>。<br><br>使用<span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span>变更武器模式。按下<span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span>发射。",
    "TencentChinese": "该武器破坏力强，适合快速击沉敌方飞船。<br><br>按 <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span> 激活。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一種<span class=\"name name-technology\">遠距離</span>太空船武器，能夠從很遠的距離發射高爆炸性的魚雷。<br><br>注意：爆炸傷害對<span class=\"name name-stellar\">無防護罩</span>的目標<span class=\"name name-stellar\">非常有效</span>，但對付<span class=\"name name-title\">有防護罩</span>的目標<span class=\"name name-title\">效果不彰</span>。<br><br>使用 <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span> 即可切換武器模式。按住 <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span> 即可開火。"
  },
